    "This makes the question of whether RLHF can truly achieve the goal of Aligned AI remains uncertain.",
    "Secondly, LLMs and RLHF pose many unpredictable ethical risks.",
    "While data filtering and RLHF can enhance the moral competence of LLMs, these methods do not solve all problems and may introduce new ones, such as bias, especially in relation to LLMs' impact on the environment and communities.",
    "Even in the context of human morality, the factors influencing human ethical behaviors are highly complex (Dewey, 1981).",
    "When faced with complex environments, LLMs will encounter greater challenges in their ethical decision-making."
